#: ../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/gui.rst:422
msgid ""
"``not (author:Asimov or author:Weber)`` finds all books not written by "
"either Asimov or Weber."
msgstr "``not (author:Asimov or author:Weber)`` vind alle boeken niet geschreven door Asimov of Weber."

